node.text:
We all know you are only as good as your team... The most important piece to my team is #family . I’m home in quarantine & wasn’t able to spend Easter with my family as many of us can relate! What does my brother do??? A creative he is indeed - @everythingrecording comes through for a fully edit Easter for my enjoyment 🙌🏻❤️
•
Edit: @everythingrecording 
Music: @everythingrecording @piggott_music @yikes_paisley

node.text: Since I was a young boy the dream has never changed. Take the company to new heights. To a place nobody ever thought was achievable or possible. Projects nobody would have ever believed could be possible. A brand that’s bigger than life. @ferrisrafauli & @champagnepapi are that reminder of where I want to be with @riverwoodbuildingcompany and a sweet reminder to myself that this is just the beginning ❤️👨🏼‍💻.
